column5: No getting stuck in the slush with this!!!!!
what the hell hahaha  I was just looking at our slushfeat photos yesterday
That is very cool...tell me it floats....please!
Brrrr.... I still tell stories about that    My therapist says I will stop having flashbacks in 3-5 years.
Wow that looks fun and dangerous lol  Me likey?
Their web site says a unit could cost well into the 100's of thousands of dollars depending on Luxury and Performance packages.  Regards, Snowball
Yep.  It's a little bit out of my price range.  Maybe I will just have to get an Argo, pound some red-bull, close my eyes and pretend.
I can't see having anytime to fish....

A quote from the MFG's website:  "Note: The Ripsaw EV2 is a handcrafted, limited run, high end luxury super tank, developed for the public and extreme off road recreation.   These vehicles take up to 6 months to fabricate and can cost well into the 100s of thousands depending on desired luxury and performance packages."
Wow, quite the machine, but I wonder what happens if you get it stuck though.
